.DT
say
Discworld player help
say

Name
.SI 5
say - Say something to people in the room.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
say <text>
'<text>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Say takes the text that is provided and gives it to all people in the same room
as you in the following format.  If you are Furball, and typed 'say hello', all
people in the room would recieve.

Furball says: hello

This is the main method of communicating on the mud.
.EP

Examples
.SI 5
> say hello
> 'hello
> say I am pleased to meet you.
> 'I am pleased to meet you.
.EI

See also
.SI 5
emote, lsay, shout, tell, whisper.
.EI
